{
  "texts": [
    "We use the same validation set and the prompt we engineered for our main model.",
    "Overall, we find considerable improvements, especially when using GPT4 for level 3.",
    "Note that the validation metrics in Table 3 do not always move in the same direction.",
    "When given the same prompt, GPT-4 is much less likely to classify in any of the dominance categories, aligning more closely with human classification.",
    "As a result, we find much higher precision and a somewhat lower recall for GPT-4."
  ]
}